        .. _Python: http://python.org
        .. _`zc.buildout`: http://buildout.org
        .. _pip: http://www.pip-installer.org
        .. _`EITB Euskal Kantak`: https://www.eitb.eus/eu/irratia/eitb-euskal-kantak/
        
